---
// src/components/manufacture/Equipment.astro
---
<section id="equipment" class="pt-12 pb-12 bg-gray-50 scroll-mt-40">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h2 class="text-[#008B9B] font-mb101 text-3xl font-bold mb-6">主要設備一覧</h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">常に高い精度を維持するための、東北ネヂの製造拠点です。</p>
        <img src="/images/factory-inner.webp" alt="工場内設備" class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-sm shadow-md" />
      </div>
      
      <div class="md:w-2/3 w-full space-y-12">
        {/* 製造能力 */}
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-[#008B9B] font-mb101 font-bold text-xl mb-6 flex items-center">
            <span class="w-2 h-6 bg-[#008B9B] mr-3"></span>◎製造能力
          </h3>
          <div class="grid gap-4 font-sans text-gray-800">
            <div class="flex border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
              <span class="w-32 font-bold">鍛造</span>
              <span>max. φ110mm、max. L＝1200mm</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
              <span class="w-32 font-bold">旋盤加工</span>
              <span>max. φ300mm、max. L＝1200mm</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
              <span class="w-32 font-bold">熱処理加工</span>
              <span>max. L＝1200mm</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* 主な材質 */}
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-[#008B9B] font-mb101 font-bold text-xl mb-6 flex items-center">
            <span class="w-2 h-6 bg-[#008B9B] mr-3"></span>◎主な材質
          </h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 border-l-4 border-[#E64A19] pl-2">JIS規格</p>
              <ul class="text-[14px] text-gray-600 space-y-1.5 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                <li>高温用合金鋼（SNB）</li>
                <li>ステンレス鋼（SUS）</li>
                <li>耐熱鋼（SUH）</li>
                <li>機械構造用合金鋼 （SCM, SNCM）</li>
                <li>機械構造用炭素鋼（SC）</li>
                <li>強度区分品 （4.6, 8.8, 10.9他）</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 border-l-4 border-[#E64A19] pl-2">その他対応規格</p>
              <p class="text-[14px] text-gray-600 font-medium mb-3">ASTM, ASME, AISI, ISO, DINなど</p>
              <p class="text-[14px] text-[#008B9B] font-bold">海外規格の実績多数</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>